long_description: we are an adaptive manufacturing e-commerce led enterprise in industry 4.0. with particular expertise in building infrastructure, digital infrastructure, artificial intelligence, digital commerce, healthcare, education, iot & transportation. as a 3rd generation, family-owned multinational company, we operate in 28 countries, across 6 continents and have an ambition to grow by 100 fold. we believe in connecting people, products, and technologies through innovation, by empowering humanity to make our world a better place. we achieve success through inspiring and empowering our leaders to achieve excellence beyond what they believe is possible – by setting world class benchmarks, caring for their development and building relationships. orient holdings was established to setup a manufacturing joint venture with clipsal australia. experienced executive business leader, with a strong track record of top and bottom line revenue growth over a 20yr career in it networking. experienced general manager with track record in generating profitable growth in both small and large companies.
generated_description: orange electric, legally known as orange electric leading electric company, based in karachi, sindh, is a multinational, family-owned enterprise specializing in adaptive manufacturing and e-commerce. the company operates in 28 countries across six continents, providing solutions in building infrastructure, digital infrastructure, artificial intelligence, digital commerce, healthcare, education, iot, and transportation. originally established in 1983 as a manufacturer of switches and sockets for clipsal australia, orange electric has expanded its portfolio significantly and now offers a wide range of products and services including energy-efficient solutions, structured cabling, network and connectivity solutions, and smart home technologies. the company is committed to innovation and social responsibility, avoiding businesses that undermine its values.
